content.original: Extreme Range ATM Ammo utilizes more advanced flight computers and stabilizer to drastically increase their range. Upon receiving a Critical Hit, any remaining ammunition stored inside an Ammo Bin will explode dealing damage to the install location. Risk can be mitigated with the use of C.A.S.E.

content.content: 极远射程ATM弹药利用更先进的飞行电脑和稳定器大幅增加其射程.在受到致命损伤后,储存在弹舱中的任何剩余弹药将爆炸,对安装部位造成伤害.使用C.A.S.E.可以降低风险.
